{"article_id":"VeBL9eOTQ5aACwRp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A classified House Intelligence Committee memo","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"viewed by Republican lawmakers Thursday","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"has been described as \" shocking \" and \" explosive \" by the congressmen","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"who read it .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"National security journalist and Fox News contributor Sara Carter reported Thursday","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"that the memo shows \" extensive Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act abuse . \"","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"The memo also reportedly contains information about the Department of Justice","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"( DOJ )","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and Federal Bureau of Investigation","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"( FBI ) ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"as well as the infamous Trump-Russia dossier .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Carter also writes","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that sources told her","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" they would not be surprised","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"if it leads to the end of Robert Mueller ' s Special Counsel investigation into President Trump and his associates . \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"She also reports","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that an unnamed congressional member told her","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" ( w ) e probably will get this stuff released by the end of the month . \"","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Texas Rep. Louie Gohmert tweeted a link to Carter ' s story shortly after its publication :","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"Read the CLASSIFIED @ HouseIntelComm memo on repeated FISA warrant abuses .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The truth may not set the guilty free","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"but it needs to come out .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Release the # FISAMemo :","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"https : //t.co/7fkXI1pl0y","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"- Louie Gohmert","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"( @ replouiegohmert )","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"January 19 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"The classified report","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"compiled by House Intelligence","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"is deeply troubling","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"and raises serious questions about the upper echelon of the Obama DOJ and Comey FBI","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"as it relates to the so-called collusion investigation .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"- Ron DeSantis","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"( @ RepDeSantis )","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"January 18 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"While the report is classified as Top Secret ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"I believe","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"the select committee should , pursuant to House rules , vote to make the report publicly available as soon as possible .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"This is a matter of national significance","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"and the American people deserve the truth .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"- Ron DeSantis","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"( @ RepDeSantis )","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"January 18 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"A number of other Republican lawmakers sounded off about the contents of the classified intelligence memo .","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"Pennsylvania Rep. Scott Perry told Fox News ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"\" You think about ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"' is this happening in America","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"or is this the KGB ? '","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"That ' s how alarming it is . \"","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Florida Rep. Matt Gaetz said ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"\" I believe","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"the consequence of its release will be major changes in people","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"currently working at the FBI and the Department of Justice . \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Gaetz also issued a statement on his congressional website Thursday","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"calling for the document to be released to the public ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"writing ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"\" The House must immediately make public the memo","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"prepared by the Intelligence Committee","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"regarding the FBI and the Department of Justice .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The facts","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"contained in this memo","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"are jaw-dropping","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and demand full transparency .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"There is no higher priority than the release of this information","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to preserve our democracy . \"","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"North Carolina Rep. Mark Meadows told Fox News ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"\" It ' s troubling .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"It is shocking .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Part of me wishes","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that I didn ' t read it","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"because I don ' t want to believe","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"that those kinds of things could be happening in this country","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that I call home","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and love so much . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":147,"left":91,"right":146,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":91,"left":77,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":78,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":82,"right":88,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":81,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":81,"left":79,"right":80,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":79,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":8,"right":9,"relati